L{f(x)} = int(exp(-s*x)*f(x),x=0..infinity);
L{f(x)} = int(exp(-s*x)*(x-5*y),x=0..infinity);
L{f(x)} = 1/s^2-5*y/s;

Case 2: f(y) := x-5*y; (x is parameter)

L{f(y)} = int(exp(-s*y)*f(y),y=0..infinity);
L{f(y)} = int(exp(-s*y)*(x-5*y),y=0..infinity);
L{f(y)} = x/s-5/s^2;

